    Shoes – Thank god for sneakers

    Since solebox was founded in 2002 in Berlin, we have always provided "state-of-the-art" in shoes. In doing so we place great value on being able of offer as wide a range of shoes as possible. From running shoes to hi-tops or Winter boots, at solebox you can find the right shoes to suit the rest of your outfit, or the weather. Limited editions and collaborations are also represented within our product range, as are the all-time classics produced by the various footwear brands. As it happens, independent shoe brands are just as well established with us as the major sportswear brands, as we always like to offer you an alternative when selecting your new shoes.

    Shoes at solebox | MBCY

    Pick your styles from our huge range of shoes, and order easily and without any hassle in the solebox | MBCY online shop. Running fans will feel just as much at home with us as basketball enthusiasts, and you can pay for your next shoes order in the solebox | MBCY online shop by advance payment, instant transfer, credit card or PayPal. Order now and enjoy affordable worldwide shipping.
